{
  "name": "RPlog_21st_of_Selona_Action",
  "title": "The Engagement of the 21st of Selona",
  "summary": "A sprawling space battle unfolds as Republic reinforcements clash with an Imperial fleet led by Captain Valerius aboard the flagship Inquisitor. The Imperial pilot Dante and her squadron tangle with starfighters while Lt. Barakzai and Commander Razem work the flagship's bridge, and the Republic commander Rasi coordinates his cruisers and the Rapier from afar. Into the chaos jumps Han Solo in the Millennium Falcon, with Chewbacca manning the quad lasers, drawn in to lend a hand and shield a stricken Republic recon ship -- the Prowler-class scout crewed by the rattled Snarl'Fashtalli, the Kasa Gienah, and Chakuro. The Falcon and Dante's fighters trade fire as the recon ship, its shields failing, scrambles to survive long enough for the Republic to maneuver and concentrate missiles on the Inquisitor's command tower. As the tide turns in the Republic's favor, Razem orders a full-speed retreat from the system and Rasi turns his attention to the battle's conclusion.",
